cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SI, cs.IR, cs.SD 

The paper deals with machine learning techniques and program synthesis to learn users' preferences in a social media setting. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), followed by cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.SI (Social and Information Networks), cs.IR (Information Retrieval), and cs.SD (Software Engineering).
